name: noresm2cmor
tagline: A command line tool for cmorizing NorESM output
body:
### Welcome to noresm2cmor's project page

noresm2cmor is a FORTRAN based command line tool for post-processing NorESM output using
the Climate Model Output Rewriter libraries.

### Support or Contact

For any questions, please write to ingo.bethke[at]uni.no.
